Package Annotator

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ComplexQueryANDAnnotator
    ComplexQueryANDAnnotator combines AtomicQueryConcept into ComplexQueryConcept.
    ComplexQueryAnnotator
    ComplexQueryAnnotator combines several AtomicQueryConcepts into a bag of words and save the string into a ComplexQueryConcept.
    ComplexQueryORAnnotator
    This complexQueryORAnnotator is used to produce OR query
    OriginalQuery
    This annotator produces query extracted from original question without any processing.
    SDAnswerGenAnnotator
    This annotator produces exact answer for each question.
    SDNERAnnotator  
    SDQuestionAnnotator
    SDQuestionAnnotator pre-processes the questions and save the terms to AtomicQuery-typed annotations.
    SDQuestionConceptAnnotator
    The SDQuestionConceptAnnotator uses OntologyServiceResponse service to process the query content and return several features which corresponds to the data type provided by project archetype.
    SDQuestionDocumentAnnotator
    The SDQuestionConceptAnnotator uses PubMedSearchServiceResponse service to process the query content and return several features which corresponds to the data type provided by project archetype.
    SDQuestionTripleAnnotator
    The SDQuestionTripleAnnotator uses LinkedLifeDataServiceResponse service to process the query content and return several features which corresponds to the data type provided by project archetype.
    SDSnippetAnnotator
    This SDSnippetAnnotator will crawl the article from the web service and divide it into multiple sentences.
    StanfordNERAnnotator
